<plot>At a dinner party with friends, David is surprised to find that Julia, the girl of his dreams is in attendance and recently available. He awkwardly excuses himself to the bathroom to freshen up. In the bathroom however, he is greeted by less than desirable circumstances and must battle to alleviate the "situation" as Julia waits patiently outside. Flush is an over the top comedy that propels human ingenuity and human frailty to new levels all in the name of love and hygiene.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?198421</url></doc>
